To create a new recipe:
  POST /recipes
	JSON:
		name: string
		imageKey: string
		description: string
		ingredients: []string
		preparationTime: int

To get all recipes:
	GET /recipes
	To get next batch:
		GET /recipes?next={id of last recipe returned}

To delete a recipe:
	DELETE /recipes/{recipe_id}

To add recipe to favorite:
	POST /favorites
	JSON:
		recipeId: string

To remove recipe from favorite:
	DELETE /favorites/{recipe_id}
	
To get all favorites recipes:
	GET /favorites
	To get next batch:
		GET /favorites?next={id of last favorite returned}

To rate a recipe:
	POST /ratings
	JSON:
		recipeId: string
		stars: int
		comment: string

To delete rating on a recipe:
	DELETE /ratings/{id of recipe}

To get all ratings on a recipe:
	GET /ratings/{id of recipe}
	To get next batch:
		GET /ratings/{id of recipe}?next_recipe={id of last recipe returned}&next_user={user id in last rating returned}

To get url to post pictures to:
	GET /upload-url